    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/8262d04f1f5771c6bdd70b16ccd03f48.poster.avif?t=1761095234\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/8262d04f1f5771c6bdd70b16ccd03f48.webm?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/8262d04f1f5771c6bdd70b16ccd03f48.mp4?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创建您自己的压铸收藏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>赚取积分以建立您自己的特殊压铸汽车收藏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/22a88dbcd3922aa7dcd54d87e7657f12.poster.avif?t=1761095234\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/22a88dbcd3922aa7dcd54d87e7657f12.webm?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/22a88dbcd3922aa7dcd54d87e7657f12.mp4?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>漂移并赚取积分</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过漂移赚取积分，用您赚取的积分购买新车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/448c86bb5601c03498cb8858c53266f6.poster.avif?t=1761095234\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/448c86bb5601c03498cb8858c53266f6.webm?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848850/extras/448c86bb5601c03498cb8858c53266f6.mp4?t=1761095234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狩猎 - 购买 -出售</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逐一浏览商店并找到稀有汽车。<br>出售您的旧车。扩大您的收藏。<br><br><strong>3D 或列表视图您的收藏</strong><br>您可以在墙上以 3D 形式查看您的收藏，也可以通过菜单列出它。您可以随时以 3D 形式详细检查您的汽车并享受它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逼真</strong><br>使用逼真的图形创建收藏时，您将获得更多乐趣。它可以帮助您感觉好像您真的购买了具有逼真图形的压铸件。您可以随时以 3D 逼真风格检查您的收藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数百种压铸模型</strong><br>多种类型的丰富车辆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>稀有和特殊物品</strong><br><br>获得非常稀有和特殊系列的令人愉快的挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为压铸收藏家</strong></h2>",
